                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Editorial Note</hi>
                </head>
                <p>At this time there were before the Fourth Committee other questions regarding
                    non-self-governing territories, apart from the issue of transmission of
                    information under Article 73(<hi rend="italic">e</hi>), that were of interest to
                    the United States. These are described briefly in the document that follows,
                    with particular reference to the position taken upon them by the United
                    States.</p>
            </div>
        </body>
